# Initialize Git repository
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial portfolio setup with Vite and Three.js"

# Create README.md file
cat > README.md << EOL
# UI/UX Designer Portfolio

## Overview
This is a modern portfolio website for UI/UX designers built with Vite and Three.js. The portfolio features interactive 3D elements, smooth animations, and a responsive design to showcase projects effectively.

## Features
- Interactive 3D hero section with Three.js
- Interactive project previews
- Smooth scrolling and animations with GSAP
- Responsive design for all devices
- Modern, clean UI

## Tech Stack
- Vite
- Three.js
- GSAP for animations
- Studio Freight Lenis for smooth scrolling

## Development
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies: \`npm install\`
3. Start development server: \`npm run dev\`
4. Build for production: \`npm run build\`

## Deployment
This site is configured for easy deployment to Cloudflare Pages.

## License
MIT
EOL